<A>__{hanna and michael are whizzing down a hill together on bicycles. he has a rucksack. it's a rural paradise hills on all sides, a gleaming river below, the sun shining brightly. she is wearing a blue dress.}
<L>__{exterior cafe. day}
<A>__{they come to a cafe and sit down outside. they pick up the menus on the table. a waitress arrives.}
